	  tlwg/Umpush.sfd, tlwg/Umpush-Oblique.sfd:
	  - Adjust trademark glyph for consistent stem widths.

	* tlwg/Umpush-Light.sfd, tlwg/Umpush-LightOblique.sfd:
	  - Add 8 glyphs for LaTeX completeness: ae, AE, oe, OE, germandbls,
	    guillemotright, questiondown, trademark. Glyphs are taken from
	    Loma, with stems made thinner.

