	* fontconfig/65-ttf-thai-tlwg.conf -> 64-ttf-thai-tlwg.conf,
	fontconfig/Makefile.am: Rank up the configuration, to really take
	precedence over fontconfig's default config.

2008-07-21  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <thep@linux.thai.net>

